_source.channelabout: The Professor's Record fights for the rights of J6 political prisoners to be free!  Stand with all January 6th, 2021 political prisoners and their families.  Resist tyranny & win back their freedom!
_source.message:
5.18.22

Lisa Eisenhart is a J6 defendant who has been put under strict house arrest and restrictive conditions for work that has greatly hampered her ability to earn an income.

Lisa has been a nurse for over three decades and her life has been exemplary, especially in nursing care for her patients.  On January 6th, she protested by walking through the Capitol.  She did not harm anyone or broke anything.

Because she was Mom to "Ziptie Guy" Eric Munchel, whom the press maligned and falsely portrayed as a violent insurrectionist, she was was imprisoned in solitary in the DC Gulag for 2 months before her release to strict house arrest. 

In today's agreement with the prosecution, Lisa is encouraged that the new prosecutor has finally approved a less restrictive measure, putting her under curfew restrictions, which allows for greater movement.

The agreement now goes to the judge for approval.  She asks for prayers for a favorable ruling!  She praises God regardless of the decision because she is greatly blessed and favored by God today despite the oppressive and unjust circumstances.

She is still prohibited from talking to her own son or anyone who was in DC on January 6th.

Please pray for Lisa today and keep remembering her in your prayers as you fast and pray for all J6 defendants and their families.

Pray for favorable rulings and negotiations before their judges and prosecutors.

Pray for freedom and justice.

Pray for strong hearts of courage to withstand the barrages of lies and smears from all fronts.

Pray for Freedom and Justice.

Pray for hope to be rekindled.

Lisa is encouraged knowing that we are fasting and praying for her and other J6 defendants and their families and is joining us in fasting and praying.

Lisa is fighting two legal battles.  A battle for her freedom.  And a related battle to not have her nursing license cancelled because she is a J6 defendant, labeled as a threat to society, a domestic terrorist.

She is currently using a public defender for J6 but has to hire an attorney for the defense of her nursing license.  Please help if you are able: https://givesendgo.com/lisaeisenhart

But prayers remain her earnest request for all of us because God has blessed Lisa with a lawyer she could currently afford with her diminished wage.
